MAIN_MESSAGE: It has been necessary for our engineers to carry out an emergency shutdown for safety at 11:32AM in the CW5 postcode area of Nantwich following reports of a grounded overhead line. This may affect the supply to your property. Our team will work to get your power back on as quickly and as safely possible by 1.45PM. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 11:33AM on 20th October 2020
